item.dc:creator: @3lv3n_snip3r 3lv3n snip3r
item.description:
@3lv3n_snip3r wrote:

[quote=“saciid.1, post:10, topic:359425”][quote author=Nebulae link=topic=455885.msg4106663#msg4106663 date=1348071926]
If someone uses a PI SoulSplit base then they definitely have the credibility to suggest they know what they are talking about.[size=1pt]lolsrs[/size]
[/quote]
Indeed[/quote]
You obviously didn’t read the fine print. The models aren’t there or are misplaced. Don’t say to change the item id, if the client couldn’t support that high of an id, it would crash the client while trying to even look at the item in-game. As for item.cfg, that wouldn’t be the problem either. Depending how you have what items go in what slot setup, you would need to add the item id in it to have it go in the correct slot and to have stats/price.
